FBIS3-36301 "drsov024_g_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-024 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Feb 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus IMF Experts Encourage Close Ties With Russia WS0402090594 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1815 GMT 3 Feb 94 WS0402090594 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Language: Belarusian Article Type:BFN [Text] Experts of the IMF, who recently visited Belarus, have encouraged the Belarusian leadership's efforts to develop close economic ties with Russia. They underlined the advantages of economic integration with Russia. At the same time, these advantages, according to expert opinions, do not imply the creation of a monetary and credit union. According to them, one should take into account the negative economic results for Belarus of the unification of the monetary and credit systems if Russia fails to secure its economic stabilization.
